    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A chance encounter with a girl who has turned into a deformed form,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The glimmer of life, the destination of sorrowful love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Larissa Elshina met a deformity with the face of her missing friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She gives it the name of Sinyaya and teaches it language. She develops feelings and grows. Like a human being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long will the cold separation, like the long winter that lies ahead, last?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Love and attachment are born in the midst of tolerance and resignation. Is it right to be human?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gaze of others always brings misfortune and drives us to fugue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What remains at the end of the girls' blue play?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313210/extras/d20b2e0c1279a7d3ae154b5f6d054c7a.avif?t=1737276558\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313210/extras_big/d20b2e0c1279a7d3ae154b5f6d054c7a.avif?t=1737276558 width=800 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sinyaya　Синяя</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313210/extras/1d127e13cbbbf9d4d182d42609f16147.avif?t=1737276558\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313210/extras_big/1d127e13cbbbf9d4d182d42609f16147.avif?t=1737276558 width=800 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Larissa Elshina　Лариса  Ельшина</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\